# Internal Claude Code session work + planning. The progress/ directory
# itself is selectively committed (RELEASE-READINESS-CHECKLIST.md,
# RISK-REGISTER*.md, HANDOFF-PROTOCOL.md are public governance records);
# the patterns below keep session-progress / internal plans / retros out
# of the public tarball + GitHub history.
progress/STATUS.md
progress/EXECUTION-PLAN.md
progress/QUALITY-ROADMAP.md
progress/retros/
progress/plans/
